description: unkempt /??n?kem(p)t/ adj. 1. lacking in order, neatness, and often cleanliness. Font designer Squid may be a bit disorderly but that didn't keep him from hand-lettering this off-kilter gem just for you. Unkempt is definitely different than your traditional regimented font but, it's hardly dirty! In fact, you can download it in a nifty little package that's never been touched by human hands. And it's fun! Get it!
